Load USA Foreign Workers.xlxs into Power BI Desktop. 8

Follow the outlined steps and GIF below:

1. Open Power BI Desktop and click on Get data

2. Select Excel File from the options

3. Upload File from your computer

4. Select both files (USA Foreign Workers.xlsx) from the desktop Display Options

5. Click on Load Data





To learn more about loading an excel workbook into Power BI, click the link below. 

https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/power-bi/connect-data/desktop-import-excel-workbooks
